Ranger Help for: gash
=====================

SYNTAX:      gash <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     75
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to deliver a powerful slashing attack that
tears through the target's defenses. The Ranger must be wielding a
slash-type weapon (sword, axe, etc.) to perform this skill. Gash deals
heavy slash damage and has a chance to cause bleeding. The damage scales
with the Ranger's strength and weapon skill. This is a mid-tier melee
attack that bridges the gap between strike and naturestrike.
